### 🛡️ 管理模块 - API 测试脚本

## 系统统计

### 获取系统统计信息
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/stats

---

## 用户管理

### 获取所有用户
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/users

---

### 获取单个用户
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/users/1

---

### 创建新用户（运营人员）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "operator_new",
  "password": "password123",
  "roleId": 2
}

---

### 创建新用户（审核员）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "reviewer_new",
  "password": "password123",
  "roleId": 3
}

---

### 更新用户
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/admin/users/7
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "operator_updated",
  "password": "newpassword123",
  "roleId": 2
}

---

### 删除用户
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/admin/users/7

---

## 角色管理

### 获取所有角色
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/roles

---

## 权限管理

### 获取所有权限
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/permissions

---

### 创建新权限
POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/permissions?permissionName=EXPORT_CONTENT

---

### 删除权限
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/admin/permissions/1

---

## 完整业务流程

### 1. 查看当前系统状态
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/stats

### 2. 查看当前用户
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/users

### 3. 创建新的运营人员
POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "operator_alice",
  "password": "alice123",
  "roleId": 2
}

### 4. 创建新的审核员
POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "reviewer_bob",
  "password": "bob123",
  "roleId": 3
}

### 5. 查看更新后的用户列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/users

### 6. 查看系统统计（应该增加了）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/stats

### 7. 更新用户角色
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/admin/users/8
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "operator_alice",
  "password": "alice123",
  "roleId": 3
}

### 8. 删除用户
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/admin/users/8

### 9. 最终统计
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/stats


